name: Covert Landing (V)
Lore: 'The stolen code allowed the Rebels to land their strike team on the Endor surface undetected - or so they thought.',
Text: 'USED: During opponent''s move phase, if Bunker ''blown away,'' peek at top four cards of a player''s Reserve Deck; replace in any order.LOST: During opponent''s move phase, deploy a Rebel scout of ability < 5 from Reserve Deck to an Endor site opponent does not occupy; reshuffle.',
